<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for your telephone call earlier notifying us of a new <i>(insert type of claim)</i>.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>In order that we can present a claim to insurers, <b>please could you fully complete and return the attached claim form</b>.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>I have attached your policy schedule and policy wordings to assist.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>I look forward to hearing from you.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>If you have any queries, please do not hesitate to contact me on <b>01242 802531</b>.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Claims Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: claims@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>